Description:
  The sentia_authentication generator sets up authlogic in application with a few options for the following
    
  --no_activation
  --no_password_reset
  --none
  
  The generator takes in 1 of 3 arguments. One to not create code for activation. Another to not create password resets code. Final option is to not 
  create activation or password_reset features
  
Examples:
    script/generate sentia_authentication
    
      Creates authlogic features and activation and password_reset functions

    script/generate sentia_authentication --no_activation
 
      Creates authlogic features and password_reset functions
 
    script/generate sentia_authentication --no_password_reset

      Creates authlogic features and activation functions

    script/generate sentia_authentication --none
    
      Creates authlogic features only
